  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0ddc\u0da9 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two killed in shooting in Ambalangoda",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ambalangoda Police say that two people have been killed in a shooting that took place in Galagoda Welapara area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda this night.",
        "The police say that a 49-year-old man named Thirimadura Vijith De Soysa, a resident of Ambalangoda Galagoda, and a 45-year-old man named Ponnahandi Ajith Sudarshana, a resident of the same address, have died.",
        "A thirty-five-year-old father of three children was killed in a shooting yesterday (26) in the Uravatta area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda.",
        "The police are investigating whether there is a connection between this shooting site and yesterday's shooting.",
        "The police say that both the shootings were carried out on motorcycles."
      ],
